&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refine and protect the Group14 and SCC55® story across B2B channels, ensuring that our messaging continues to define the silicon battery space globally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate messaging across our hubs in the U.S., South Korea, and Germany, accounting for local market nuances and regulatory environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Position our executive leadership as the definitive voices on silicon battery technology and the global energy transition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work alongside legal and executive teams to communicate our impact on domestic supply chains and national energy security to government stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source (as needed) and manage external vendors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support communications surrounding government grants, tax credits, and partnerships (e.g., DOE initiatives) that fuel our manufacturing expansion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide hands-on coaching, or outside resources, to prepare executives to navigate high stakes communications confidently. This may include preparing for interviews, videos, internal and external presentations, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a robust framework for managing reputation risks inherent in rapid global scaling and industrial manufacturing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus on pull-through demand by highlighting how SCC55® empowers our customers&#39; innovations in EVs, consumer electronics, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In partnership with People &amp;amp; Culture, foster a unified culture across our global factories to ensure every employee is an ambassador for our mission.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE’RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12+ years in corporate communications or marketing, specifically within deep-tech, energy, or advanced manufacturing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Communications, International Relations, or Business; MBA or relevant advanced degree preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
